name: Missile-fly
description: I make not-so-traditional mandalas. Each one has a very specific energy and intention put into it. You can use it as a wallpaper on your screen or print it out and hang it on your wall and it will have positive effect on your psyche. This one is alien butterfly that has some weight problems :D...or not, it can suck all the excess weight out of you, cause travel between different dimensions requires lot of energy.
